# Privacy Policy

_Last updated: {{current_date}}_

## Information We Collect
- Game scores and progress (stored locally on your device)
- App usage analytics (anonymous)
- Ad interaction data (managed by Google AdMob)
- Device information for ad serving

## How We Use Information
- To save your game progress and high scores
- To improve app performance and user experience
- To display relevant advertisements
- To provide technical support when requested

## Data Storage and Security
- Game data is stored locally on your device
- We do not store personal information on our servers
- Analytics data is anonymized and aggregated
- We use industry-standard security measures

## Third-Party Services
- Google AdMob for advertisement serving
- Google Analytics for app usage statistics
- These services have their own privacy policies
- You can opt out of personalized ads in your device settings

## Children's Privacy
Our app is designed to be family-friendly. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. All advertisements are family-safe and appropriate for all ages.

## Your Rights
- Delete app data by uninstalling the app
- Opt out of personalized ads in device settings
- Contact us with privacy concerns
- Request information about data we collect

## Contact Us
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: **alidiplana@gmail.com**

